{"title":"Python学习笔记_4列表和元组的区别","slug":"Python学习笔记_4：列表和元组的区别","date":"2020-06-17","updated":"2020-07-08","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/44475.json","excerpt":"<p>上节我主要详细的介绍了一下列表的用法</p><p>突然想起来需要说一下列表和元组的区别,所以这篇文章就简洁点,以文字为主</p><p><strong>列表:存放的是暂时的元素,可以更改,增添</strong></p><p><strong>元组:存放的是不可更改的元素,不可删除,不可添加,不可修改</strong></p>","cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200304212858622.png","covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200304212858622.png"],"content":"<p>上节我主要详细的介绍了一下列表的用法</p>\n<p>突然想起来需要说一下列表和元组的区别,所以这篇文章就简洁点,以文字为主</p>\n<p><strong>列表:存放的是暂时的元素,可以更改,增添</strong></p>\n<p><strong>元组:存放的是不可更改的元素,不可删除,不可添加,不可修改</strong></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>list ( [ string ] )：将 str 转化为列表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>exmp = <span class=\"string\">'abcd efgh'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>list(exmp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出为</span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">'a'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'b'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'c'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'d'</span>, <span class=\"string\">' '</span>, <span class=\"string\">'e'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'f'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'g'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'h'</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>tuple ( [ string ] )：将 str 转化为元组</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>exmp = <span class=\"string\">'abcd efgh'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>tuple(exmp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出为</span><br><span class=\"line\">(<span class=\"string\">'a'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'b'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'c'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'d'</span>, <span class=\"string\">' '</span>, <span class=\"string\">'e'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'f'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'g'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'h'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>当我们的项目中需要一些永远不用更改的数据,那就用元组</p>\n<p>如果我们需要后期维护并修改时就用列表</p>\n<p>但是在一定条件下我们需要改变元组中的数据或者增添一些新元素难道就没办法了嘛?<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200304212858622.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>当然不是,我们可以新建一个元组来代替原来的元组啊….是不是方法很沙雕</p>\n<p>不过在这里要说一个关于在元组之中添加元素的方法</p>\n<p>比如要在下列元组的’B’’E’中添加’C’’D’</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = (<span class=\"string\">'A'</span>,<span class=\"string\">'B'</span>,<span class=\"string\">'E'</span>,<span class=\"string\">'F'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = I[<span class=\"number\">0</span>:<span class=\"number\">2</span>]+(<span class=\"string\">'C'</span>,<span class=\"string\">'D'</span>)+I[<span class=\"number\">2</span>:]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print(I)</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出为</span><br><span class=\"line\">(<span class=\"string\">'A'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'B'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'C'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'D'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'E'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'F'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这样如果在遇到紧急需要处理的问题时能省事的解决</p>\n<p>但如果真的要对元组改动太大</p>\n<p>那只能新建一个元组了,所以我们一般不太会使用元组。</p>\n","url":"/posts/44475/","min2read":1,"word4post":400,"prev_post":{"title":"Python学习笔记_5：字符串格式化符号及进制转换","url":"/posts/22649/"},"next_post":{"title":"Python学习笔记_3：python 列表的使用方法—详细","url":"/posts/36135/"},"toc":"","categories":[{"name":"python","path":"api/categories/python.json","url":"/categories/python/"},{"name":"语法笔记","path":"api/categories/语法笔记.json","url":"/categories/python/语法笔记/"}],"tags":[{"name":"python","path":"api/tags/python.json","url":"/tags/python/"},{"name":"语法笔记","path":"api/tags/语法笔记.json","url":"/tags/语法笔记/"}]}